ed on and then you wait more hoping root will last longer this time. Necro's do not have a pet to help kill the critter and 2min is a long time waiting for the dot's to finish off the critter, and in most the higher lvl critters you have to reaply the same dot's to kill it.<BR>Necro's have the best mana regen in the game, and of course it comes at a price, your health.You have to keep a carefull balance with this because if you get to low and root breaks, your in trouble.<BR>I know I missed some things in this post and I appologize, but what it comes down to is yes the mage needs to be fixed, Id like to see them get a root and give the earth elemental something else.But all the int. casters with the exception of the enchanter are screwed post 50.The necro in groups under 4 is usefull, but when its 5+ the usefullness quickly diminishes.
